-- CBS Says NCAA Basketball Championship Draws 21 Million Viewers
-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 2012-04-03T19:09:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-03/cbs-says-ncaa-basketball-championship-draws-21-million-viewers.html
CBS Corp. (CBS)  said its broadcast of the
men’s college basketball championship game last night, won by
the  University of Kentucky , averaged 20.9 million viewers, a 4
percent gain from last year’s finale.  Kentucky ’s victory over the University of  Kansas  drew the
second-biggest audience for the championship in the last seven
years, New York-based CBS said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andy Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
